# Loan Data Engineering Pipeline

This project implements a complete Data Engineering pipeline using PySpark and Azure Data Lake.

Architecture:
Bronze → Silver → Gold

Technologies:
- PySpark
- Azure Data Lake Storage
- Parquet
- Python
- Spark SQL

Pipeline Steps:
1. Raw data ingestion (Bronze)
2. Data cleaning and transformation (Silver)
3. Star schema modeling (Gold)

Tables:
- dim_customer
- dim_region
- dim_loan_type
- dim_date
- fact_loans